vulnerabilities.title: Missing Security Headers
vulnerabilities.description: The server is missing 7 security header(s): X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options, X-XSS-Protection, Strict-Transport-Security, Content-Security-Policy, Referrer-Policy, Permissions-Policy
vulnerabilities.recommendation: Add security headers to prevent clickjacking, MIME sniffing, and XSS attacks.
